{"id":80741,"date":"2022-06-20T09:18:09","date_gmt":"2022-06-20T07:18:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=80741"},"modified":"2022-09-25T13:21:17","modified_gmt":"2022-09-25T11:21:17","slug":"medellin-colombia","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/medellin-colombia\/","title":{"rendered":"13 Best Things to do in Medellin, Colombia"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Medellin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In Medellin, Colombia, you can be walking among towering skyscrapers, enjoying a coffee on the terrace of a chic sky bar in the morning. By afternoon, you can be flying in a gondola over the dense forest and traditional villages. Some of the top things to do in Medellin are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-1-el-poblado\">1. El Poblado<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>El Poblado is a beautiful district full of green parks, rivers, and edgy industrial buildings covered in plants. This area is known as one of the most wealthy in the city, where foreigners and tourists tend to hang out. Because of that, it&#x2019;s not the most authentic place in Medellin, but it is a safe area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44.jpg\" alt=\"El Poblado medellin street art\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"El Poblado medellin street art\" class=\"wp-image-83885 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u