out on one side and a quieter, more &#x2018;family friendly&#x2019; neighborhood on the other. Located on a small hill, the district can be walked around in 20 minutes; this is the perfect amount of time to explore the colorful neighborhood, its art, and some of the best restaurants in Medellin, Colombia.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/el-poblado-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a hotel in El Poblado<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15150239\/medellin-colombia-40.jpg\" alt=\"best place to stay medellin colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best place to stay medellin colombia\" class=\"wp-image-83889 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15150239\/medellin-colombia-40.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15150239\/medellin-colombia-40-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15150239\/medellin-colombia-40-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15150239\/medellin-colombia-40-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20