\">Bike Tour, Medellin<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A bike tour in Medellin is the perfect way to learn about different neighborhoods in the city. You&#x2019;ll follow an experienced guide as you cycle via the city&#x2019;s main sights&#x2014;for example, Plaza Botero, the Memory Museum, the Palace of Culture, and the brand-new park. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39.jpg\" alt=\"things to do medellin bike tour \"><\/noscript><img width=\"260\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do medellin bike tour \" class=\"wp-image-83819 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1476px) 100vw, 1476px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39.jpg 1476w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-461x600.jpg 461w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-623x810.jpg 623w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-260x338.jpg 260w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-125x163.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-138x180.jpg 138w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-590x768.jpg 590w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-787x1024.jpg 787w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13190212\/medellin-colombia-39-830x1080.jpg 830w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u