\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s a somber story that pushes the community forward as they lead the neighborhood into the future. The district is now known as one of the most creative in Medellin, with its urban art, graffiti, dancing locals, rap artists, painters, and storytellers. There&#x2019;s no doubt that the arts have had enormous influence here, changing the lives of the locals.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8.jpg\" alt=\"street art medellin colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"street art medellin colombia\" class=\"wp-image-83735 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-438x600.jpg 438w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-591x810.jpg 591w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-246x338.jpg 246w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-131x180.jpg 131w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-560x768.jpg 560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-747x1024.jpg 747w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-788x1080.jpg 788w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-1050x1440.jpg 1050w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-300x411.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-600x823.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-150x206.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165719\/medellin-colombia-8.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>How to Get Around Comuna 13<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Comuna is very steep and hilly. To reach the top of the Comuna, jump on the escalator or take the cable car. This is the only public car in South America, costing a grand total of 6 million dollars! However, this was a high price to pay, not only financially but also to the community, as to build the cable car, the government tore many houses down. It&#x2019;s another story to remember when enjoying what is now a beautiful place in Medellin, Colombia.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2