ontent\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15151012\/medellin-colombia-46.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>Walking Tour in Comuna 13<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Comuna 13 is very safe these days, but we still recommend a free walking tour with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.zippytourcomuna13.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Zippy Tours<\/a> (one of the top things to do in Medellin!). It&#x2019;s run by local guides who live there (or have lived there) themselves, so they can give you the inside scoop on life in the neighborhood. It&#x2019;s a super interesting tour, where you can better understand the horrific history, the strong community, and the stories behind the influential murals and graffiti in the area. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13.jpg\" alt=\"Comuna 13 street art medellin\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Comuna 13 street art medellin\" class=\"wp-image-83745 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10165831\/medellin-colombia-13.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Please leave a reasonable tip for the guide. They run these tours based on donations, and these will go directly to graffiti artists and activities for the local children.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Fun fact:<\/strong> The houses in Comuna 13 are not painted. This is because once they&#x2019;re painted, they are considered &#x2018;finished&#x2019;, and the owner will have to start paying tax.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/80741&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/18115706\/things-to-do-medellin-colombia-4.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/18115706\/things-to-do-medellin-colombia-4-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/18115706\/things-to-do-medellin-colombia-4-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"13 Best Things to do in Medellin, Colombia\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-5-castle-museum\">5. Castle Museum<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the unique things to do in Medellin, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a>, is to visit the Castle Museum. This gothic-style residence is more reminiscent of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/czech-republic\/castles-czech-republic\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">castles in the Czech Republic<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">France<\/a>, making you feel a world away from Colombian city life. The castle was built in 1930 for a wealthy Colombian to live in but is now a museum open to the public, where you can see classic furniture, traditional paintings, and glassware.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Do not skip the tropical vibes and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/cartagena-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">colonial buildings of Cartagena, Colombia<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1.jpg\" alt=\"Castle Museum medellin\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Castle Museum medellin\" class=\"wp-image-83904 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/1