:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Not only can you see a lot of beautiful artifacts, but you can enjoy the calming gardens full of flowers, water fountains, and singing birds. There&#x2019;s also the option to enjoy the castle cafe and its delicious coffee, tea, and cakes. Alternatively, join the many other picnickers in the garden at the weekends!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Castle Tour<\/strong>: Castle can be visited inside; a guided tour is included in the regular entrance ticket of 18000 COP (~ 4.5 USD).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-83770 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/12170443\/medellin-colombia-21-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c