ver the valley and the islands and lakes of Guatape; it should take you around 20 minutes to the top. It reminded us of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sigiriya-lion-rock\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sigiriya Rock<\/a> in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also visit:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tatacoa-desert\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tatacoa Desert: Colombia&#x2019;s Best Kept Secret<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13135553\/medellin-colombia-25.jpg\" alt=\"Piedra del Pe&#xF1;ol guatape medeillin things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"277\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Piedra del Pe&#xF1;ol guatape medeillin things to do\" class=\"wp-image-83782 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1574px) 100vw, 1574px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13135553\/medellin-colombia-25.jpg 1574w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13135553\/medellin-colombia-25-492x600.jpg 492w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13135553\/medellin-colombia-25-664x810.jpg 664w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13135553\/medellin-colombia-25-2