 every day of the year from 8 AM &#x2013; 6 PM and costs 20,000 pesos (5.50 USD) per person to climb. The rock is only 10 minutes from the village and can be reached by Colombian tuk-tuk (Motachiva) or by car (there is parking for a small fee below the rock). The rock is incredibly popular, so we recommend visiting outside of traffic hours (early in the morning) and avoiding weekends.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"67324P1,70874P3,112814P8\" data-vi-campaign=\"medellin-colombia-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do medellin Piedra del Pe&#xF1;ol guatape\"><\/noscript><img width=\"255\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do medellin Piedra del Pe&#xF1;ol guatape\" class=\"wp-image-83785 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1449px) 100vw, 1449px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26.jpg 1449w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26-453x600.jpg 453w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26-611x810.jpg 611w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26-255x338.jpg 255w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13141733\/medellin-colombia-26-123x163.jpg 123w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\