pg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15143215\/medellin-colombia-42-150x217.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15143215\/medellin-colombia-42-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15143215\/medellin-colombia-42.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-nightlife-in-medellin-colombia\">8. Nightlife&#xA0;in Medellin, Colombia<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The nightlife in Medellin is one of the best in the whole of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a>, home to colorful bars, rooftops, and a buzzing atmosphere. Go with the people from your hostel and discover the many places for going out in the city. Plus, during the day, the same area transforms into nice cafes. Some of our favorites were:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Berlin Bar<\/strong> <\/li><li><strong>La Octava Bar<\/strong> (ball pit!)<\/li><li><strong>Vintrash<\/strong>&#xA0;<\/li><li><strong>Rooftops<\/strong> (best views can be found at Los Patios Hostel and Envy Rooftop)<\/li><li><strong>Parque Lleras<\/strong> (a nice park surrounded by bars and nightclubs, including Envy Rooftop and Woka Lounge)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Want an alternative night out? Join one of the traditional Chivas (party buses), which are very typical in Colombia.&#xA0; The buses play loud music and have flashing lights, carrying people through the streets and making stops at bars along the way.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38.jpg\" alt=\"party medellin\"><\/noscript><img width=\"232\" height=\"338\" alt=\"party medellin\" class=\"wp-image-83810 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1318px) 100vw, 1318px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38.jpg 1318w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-412x600.jpg 412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-556x810.jpg 556w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-232x338.jpg 232w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-112x163.jpg 112w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-124x180.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colombia-38-527x768.jpg 527w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13163428\/medellin-colo