=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/salento-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">world&#x2019;s tallest palm trees at Salento, Colombia<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7.jpg\" alt=\"things to do medellin colombia Botanical gardens\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do medellin colombia Botanical gardens\" class=\"wp-image-83728 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1361px) 100vw, 1361px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7.jpg 1361w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-425x600.jpg 425w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-574x810.jpg 574w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-544x768.jpg 544w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-726x1024.jpg 726w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-766x1080.jpg 766w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10142115\/medellin-colombia-7-1021x1440.jpg 1021w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha