ferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a>. Some absolute must-sees in Medellin are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Memory House Museum<\/strong> (history museum with exhibits on previous Colombian wars and conflicts)<\/li><li><strong>Parque Explora<\/strong> (interactive science museum and also home to South America&#x2019;s largest freshwater aquarium)<\/li><li><strong>Museo de Antioquia<\/strong> (art museum that houses a large amount of Botero&#x2019;s work)<\/li><li><strong>Museo de Arte Moderno<\/strong> (a modern art museum in a refurbished industrial building)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Please note that most museums in Medellin are closed on a Monday.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13191320\/medellin-colombia-41.jpg\" alt=\"best museum medellin colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best museum medellin colombia\" class=\"wp-image-83823 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13191320\/medellin-colombia-41.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13191320\/medellin-colombia-41-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13191320\/medellin-colombia-41-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13191320\