eaper areas in the city, such as Laureles, which is less touristy but still very safe.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-medellin\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Medellin.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-popular-hostels\">Popular hostels<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/los-patios-hostel-medellin\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Los Patios Hostel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090726\/lospatiosmedellin-450x281.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Los Patios Hostel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/rango-hostel-boutique\/\" target=\"_bl